org.cryptacular.bean

Class ResourceBasedPublicKeyFactoryBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cryptacular.bean.ResourceBasedPublicKeyFactoryBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FactoryBean<PublicKey>

    public class ResourceBasedPublicKeyFactoryBean
extends Object
implements FactoryBean<PublicKey>
    Factory for creating a public key from a Resource containing data in any of the formats supported by KeyPairUtil.readPublicKey(java.io.InputStream).
    Author:
    Middleware Services
    See Also:
    KeyPairUtil.readPublicKey(java.io.InputStream)
